{
  "chapter": 264,
  "chapter_summary": "项少龙因失血过多脸色苍白，解子元前来探望并邀他同往玉兰楼。项少龙先到解府拜访善柔，告知被曹秋道刺伤之事。随后两人前往玉兰楼，项少龙以沈良身份出现。在楼中，兰宫媛为解子元的新曲演唱，仲孙玄华亦在场。项少龙小憩时，兰宫媛轻声咏唱，令他恍若入梦。仲孙玄华试探项少龙的飞刀绝技，项少龙婉拒。此时吕不韦携齐雨、韩竭、旦楚到来，吕不韦一眼认出项少龙却不揭破。双方暗中交锋，吕不韦意图挑起仲孙家与项少龙的嫌隙，又暗示沈良身份以借刀杀人。项少龙沉着应对，化解危机。吕不韦试图约见项少龙，被以\"相见不如不见\"回绝。解子元在项少龙提醒下赶回家中。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_jie_zi_yuan",
      "speaker_name": "解子元",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "你怎会忽然病得脸无人色似的，小弟还想找你去逛逛呢！",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 264,
      "line_start": 2,
      "line_end": 3
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_jie_zi_yuan",
      "text": "你的事解决了吗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 264,
      "line_start": 6,
      "line_end": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jie_zi_yuan",
      "speaker_name": "解子元",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "就算解决不了，小弟都要为兰宫媛写成最后压轴的一曲，这次糟了，最怕大王怪责我。",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 264,
      "line_start": 8,
      "line_end": 9
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_jie_zi_yuan",
      "text": "只有五天时间，怎办好呢？你自己去不行吗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 264,
      "line_start": 12,
      "line_end": 13
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jie_zi_yuan",
      "speaker_name": "解子元",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "内子只信任你一个人，我若不带你回家给她过目，什么地方都去不了。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 264,
      "line_start": 16,
      "line_end": 16
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_jie_zi_yuan",
      "text": "你说要去仲孙龙处商量要事不就成嘛！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 264,
      "line_start": 20,
      "line_end": 20
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jie_zi_yuan",
      "speaker_name": "解子元",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "仲孙玄华那家伙怎敢瞒她，只消她问一句就知我在说谎。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 264,
      "line_start": 22,
      "line_end": 22
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_jie_zi_yuan",
      "text": "那小弟只好舍命陪君子，抱病和你去胡混吧！",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 264,
      "line_start": 26,
      "line_end": 27
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shan_rou",
      "speaker_name": "善柔",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "发生什么事？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 264,
      "line_start": 34,
      "line_end": 35
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_shan_rou",
      "text": "给你的师父刺了一剑。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 264,
      "line_start": 38,
      "line_end": 38
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shan_rou",
      "speaker_name": "善柔",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "什么？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 264,
      "line_start": 40,
      "line_end": 40
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jie_zi_yuan",
      "speaker_name": "解子元",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "我们到兰宫媛的玉兰楼去，这妮子对我应有点意思。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 264,
      "line_start": 44,
      "line_end": 45
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_jie_zi_yuan",
      "text": "今晚全听解兄的吩咐。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 264,
      "line_start": 48,
      "line_end": 48
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jie_zi_yuan",
      "speaker_name": "解子元",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "只要我告诉柔骨美人今晚是为了作曲而到她那里去，怎样没空她都要来向我献媚的。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 264,
      "line_start": 52,
      "line_end": 52
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_jie_zi_yuan",
      "text": "别忘记初更前回家，否则没人可救得了你。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 264,
      "line_start": 56,
      "line_end": 56
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jie_zi_yuan",
      "speaker_name": "解子元",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "小弟到青楼去，只是想感受那种烟花地的气氛，用以提起心思，绝非有什么不轨企图，有这么的两个时辰尽可够乐了！",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 264,
      "line_start": 58,
      "line_end": 59
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_jie_zi_yuan",
      "text": "原来如此，我放心了。",
      "tone": "欣慰",
      "chapter": 264,
      "line_start": 62,
      "line_end": 62
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_jie_zi_yuan",
      "text": "还在为政事心烦吗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 264,
      "line_start": 66,
      "line_end": 66
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jie_zi_yuan",
      "speaker_name": "解子元",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "说不心烦是违心之言，今早我见过二王子，唉！这些是不该对你说的。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 264,
      "line_start": 68,
      "line_end": 70
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jie_zi_yuan",
      "speaker_name": "解子元",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "到了！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 264,
      "line_start": 72,
      "line_end": 72
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_jie_zi_yuan",
      "text": "为何楼内的人像对解兄非常熟络和巴结的样子？",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 264,
      "line_start": 80,
      "line_end": 80
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jie_zi_yuan",
      "speaker_name": "解子元",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "一来小弟的作品乃这里必备的曲目，二来我昨晚特别请仲孙龙给我在这里订房，于临淄谁敢不给他面子。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 264,
      "line_start": 82,
      "line_end": 83
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "兰夫人",
      "listener": "char_jie_zi_yuan",
      "text": "媛媛知道解大人肯来探她，开心得什么人都忘记。刻下正沐浴打扮，立即就来，解大人和沈爷要不要多点两个女儿来增添热闹？",
      "tone": "娇声",
      "chapter": 264,
      "line_start": 86,
      "line_end": 88
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jie_zi_yuan",
      "speaker_name": "解子元",
      "listener": "char_lan_fu_ren",
      "text": "不用了！我们是专程为媛小姐来的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 264,
      "line_start": 96,
      "line_end": 97
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "兰夫人",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "媛媛今晚是解大人的，沈爷要不要奴家为你挑个好女儿呢？",
      "tone": "娇声",
      "chapter": 264,
      "line_start": 104,
      "line_end": 105
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_lan_fu_ren",
      "text": "在下今晚只是来做陪客。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 264,
      "line_start": 108,
      "line_end": 108
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jie_zi_yuan",
      "speaker_name": "解子元",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "曲既精彩，媛小姐又唱得好，玄华佩服佩服！",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 264,
      "line_start": 128,
      "line_end": 129
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jie_zi_yuan",
      "speaker_name": "解子元",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "沈兄醒来了，我们喝一杯，今晚不醉无归。",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 264,
      "line_start": 134,
      "line_end": 134
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_gong_yuan",
      "speaker_name": "兰宫媛",
      "listener": "char_jie_zi_yuan",
      "text": "不准解大人提这个'归'字，今晚让人家好好伺候你嘛！",
      "tone": "娇声",
      "chapter": 264,
      "line_start": 138,
      "line_end": 139
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "小弟睡了多久？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 264,
      "line_start": 144,
      "line_end": 144
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhong_sun_xuan_hua",
      "speaker_name": "仲孙玄华",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "我来了足有整个时辰，沈兄一直睡着。若非媛小姐肯开金口，否则怕谁都唤不醒沈兄。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 264,
      "line_start": 146,
      "line_end": 148
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhong_sun_xuan_hua",
      "speaker_name": "仲孙玄华",
      "listener": "char_jie_zi_yuan",
      "text": "佳人配才子，小弟从未见过媛小姐肯这么顺从人意，小弟便从未尝过媛小姐这种温柔滋味。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 264,
      "line_start": 154,
      "line_end": 155
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhong_sun_xuan_hua",
      "speaker_name": "仲孙玄华",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "家父对沈兄的飞刀绝技念念不忘，不知小弟能否有一开眼界的机会？",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 264,
      "line_start": 160,
      "line_end": 161
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_zhong_sun_xuan_hua",
      "text": "至少要待小弟病愈才成。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 264,
      "line_start": 164,
      "line_end": 164
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhong_sun_xuan_hua",
      "speaker_name": "仲孙玄华",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "这个当然。哈！沈兄该正是鸿运当头，有解大人这位好朋友。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 264,
      "line_start": 168,
      "line_end": 168
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_gong_yuan",
      "speaker_name": "兰宫媛",
      "listener": "char_zhong_sun_xuan_hua",
      "text": "什么飞刀之技？仲孙公子不要打哑谜似的好吗？",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 264,
      "line_start": 172,
      "line_end": 172
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jie_zi_yuan",
      "speaker_name": "解子元",
      "listener": "char_lan_gong_yuan",
      "text": "只是一场误会，媛小姐知否沈兄是凤大小姐的团管事。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 264,
      "line_start": 174,
      "line_end": 174
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "兰夫人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "奴家想借媛媛片刻光景，请三位大爷给奴家少许面子，万勿介意。",
      "tone": "娇声",
      "chapter": 264,
      "line_start": 180,
      "line_end": 180
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_gong_yuan",
      "speaker_name": "兰宫媛",
      "listener": "char_lan_fu_ren",
      "text": "他们不介意，奴家可介意呢！不过兰姨这么疼媛媛，媛媛怎么介意，也都要勉为其难！",
      "tone": "娇声",
      "chapter": 264,
      "line_start": 184,
      "line_end": 184
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhong_sun_xuan_hua",
      "speaker_name": "仲孙玄华",
      "listener": "char_lan_fu_ren",
      "text": "是否齐雨兄来了？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 264,
      "line_start": 190,
      "line_end": 190
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "兰夫人",
      "listener": "char_zhong_sun_xuan_hua",
      "text": "仲孙公子一猜就中，来的尚有秦国的大人物吕大相国。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 264,
      "line_start": 192,
      "line_end": 192
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhong_sun_xuan_hua",
      "speaker_name": "仲孙玄华",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "若论秦国的人物，首推项少龙，吕不韦嘛！哼！",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 264,
      "line_start": 196,
      "line_end": 198
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_gong_yuan",
      "speaker_name": "兰宫媛",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "妾身打个招呼，立即回来。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 264,
      "line_start": 200,
      "line_end": 200
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jie_zi_yuan",
      "speaker_name": "解子元",
      "listener": "char_lan_gong_yuan",
      "text": "媛小姐不用介怀，在下亦到回家的时候了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 264,
      "line_start": 204,
      "line_end": 205
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_gong_yuan",
      "speaker_name": "兰宫媛",
      "listener": "char_jie_zi_yuan",
      "text": "妾身不会让公子走的，若是这样，人家留在这里好了。",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 264,
      "line_start": 208,
      "line_end": 208
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_gong_yuan",
      "speaker_name": "兰宫媛",
      "listener": "char_lan_fu_ren",
      "text": "仲父那边来了多少人？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 264,
      "line_start": 212,
      "line_end": 212
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_lan_gong_yuan",
      "text": "媛小姐不去招呼一下，那可不大好吧！",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 264,
      "line_start": 214,
      "line_end": 214
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "兰夫人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "仲父闻得解大人和仲孙公子在这里，正要过来打招呼！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 264,
      "line_start": 218,
      "line_end": 218
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "小弟有点头晕脚软，先一步告退，三位请了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 264,
      "line_start": 222,
      "line_end": 223
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "兰夫人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "真巧呢！奴家是刚好碰见仲父和三位大人走过来呢！",
      "tone": "娇声",
      "chapter": 264,
      "line_start": 232,
      "line_end": 232
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_lv_bu_wei",
      "text": "沈良见过仲父！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 264,
      "line_start": 236,
      "line_end": 237
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_bu_wei",
      "speaker_name": "吕不韦",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "沈先生像极吕不韦的一位故友，真给吓了一跳。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 264,
      "line_start": 240,
      "line_end": 240
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_gong_yuan",
      "speaker_name": "兰宫媛",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "沈爷为何又不走了？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 264,
      "line_start": 256,
      "line_end": 257
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_lan_gong_yuan",
      "text": "这么走太没礼貌了。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 264,
      "line_start": 260,
      "line_end": 260
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_bu_wei",
      "speaker_name": "吕不韦",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "凤小姐有沈良兄为她打理团务，实是她的福气！",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 264,
      "line_start": 262,
      "line_end": 263
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_lv_bu_wei",
      "text": "哪里哪里，小弟只是量力而为！",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 264,
      "line_start": 266,
      "line_end": 266
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "兰夫人",
      "listener": "char_lv_bu_wei",
      "text": "仲父和沈先生是否素识？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 264,
      "line_start": 274,
      "line_end": 274
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_bu_wei",
      "speaker_name": "吕不韦",
      "listener": "char_lan_fu_ren",
      "text": "确曾有过来往，异地重逢，教人意想不到。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 264,
      "line_start": 276,
      "line_end": 277
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_lv_bu_wei",
      "text": "今趟来临淄，哪想得到会见到这么多老朋友。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 264,
      "line_start": 282,
      "line_end": 282
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhong_sun_xuan_hua",
      "speaker_name": "仲孙玄华",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "沈兄原来相识满天下，难怪与韩侯和龙阳君那么稔熟。",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 264,
      "line_start": 298,
      "line_end": 298
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "都是各位给的面子，小弟敬各位一杯。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 264,
      "line_start": 308,
      "line_end": 308
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_bu_wei",
      "speaker_name": "吕不韦",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "沈兄这两天是否有空，可否找个时间再碰碰头，又或吕某亲来拜候？",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 264,
      "line_start": 312,
      "line_end": 312
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_lv_bu_wei",
      "text": "相见不如不见，仲父三思才好。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 264,
      "line_start": 320,
      "line_end": 320
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_bu_wei",
      "speaker_name": "吕不韦",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "沈良毕竟是沈良，那天吕某听到沈先生独闯仲孙府，早该猜到沈先生是故人。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 264,
      "line_start": 328,
      "line_end": 329
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_zhong_sun_xuan_hua",
      "text": "那天全赖仲孙兄的令尊高抬贵手，又有李相爷在旁说项，否则小弟恐难在这里喝酒和听媛小姐的仙曲了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 264,
      "line_start": 340,
      "line_end": 341
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhong_sun_xuan_hua",
      "speaker_name": "仲孙玄华",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "哪里哪里，只是一场小误会！",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 264,
      "line_start": 344,
      "line_end": 344
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jie_zi_yuan",
      "speaker_name": "解子元",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "真的只是小小误会，大家把这杯喝了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 264,
      "line_start": 348,
      "line_end": 348
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jie_zi_yuan",
      "speaker_name": "解子元",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "各位见谅，小弟要赶回家去了！",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 264,
      "line_start": 360,
      "line_end": 360
    }
  ],
